            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1632826705064-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> Tenderstem broccoli</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1632826708447-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1632826708447-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1632826708447-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1632826708447-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1632826708447-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> medium egg noodles </strong>and<strong> halved Tenderstem broccoli </strong>to a pot and cover with <strong>boiled water</strong> until fully submerged</p><p>Bring to the boil and cook over a high heat for 5 min or until the noodles are cooked and the broccoli is tender</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>noodles & broccoli</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy noodle water</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1632826711759-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1632826711759-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1632826711759-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1632826711759-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1632826711759-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free mince has started to brown, add the <strong>sticky stir-fry sauce </strong>to the pan with<strong> half</strong> the<strong> sliced spring onion</strong> (save the rest for later!) and cook for 3-4 min or until the meat-free mince is cooked through</p><p>Add the <strong>drained noodles</strong> <strong>& broccoli</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>sticky meat-free mince & broccoli noodle stir-fry</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy noodle water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1632826714259-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1632826714259-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1632826714259-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1632826714259-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1632826714259-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sticky meat-free mince & broccoli noodle stir-fry</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining sliced spring onion</strong> and your <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
